294
00:47:33,502 --> 00:47:39,030
He wants you
to initiate the response.

295
00:47:40,596 --> 00:47:43,773
Ask help from no one.

296
00:48:02,488 --> 00:48:04,490
They will all betray you.

297
00:48:05,970 --> 00:48:08,668
