what happened to my brother?

299
00:48:16,241 --> 00:48:18,243
[woman] He has risen.

300
00:48:18,286 --> 00:48:20,506
He sits with his father now.

301
00:49:00,546 --> 00:49:04,550
- [footsteps]
- [breathing heavily]

